---
title: Creamy Truffle Chicken & Roast Veggie Soup with Garlic Butter Panini
description: A creamy soup at the end of the day is a great way to reset. Try this one with chicken and roasted veggies for those classic flavours but amp up the wow factor with our herb and mushroom seasoning. Those aromas are already warming us up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-truffle-chicken-roast-veggie-soup-36b6d318.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/creamy-truffle-chicken-roast-veggie-soup-64545a407c6d253bd709d714-aeab7102.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
